","desc":"佐藤正治"},{"id":37449,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/28/a8/37449_crt_H2spZ.jpg","name":"哆啦咪子","desc":"皆口裕子"},{"id":37443,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/03/67/37443_crt_UuXFE.jpg","name":"哆啦尼可夫","desc":"配角"}],"staff":[{"id":1523,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/5e/da/1523_prsn_fsFvc.jpg","name":"藤子·F·不二雄","desc":"原作"},{"id":1270,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/46/76/1270_prsn_rkccC.jpg","name":"米谷良知","desc":"导演"},{"id":21515,"image":"","name":"善聪一郎","desc":"演出"},{"id":2261,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/74/27/2261_prsn_TAc8H.jpg","name":"宫崎慎二","desc":"音乐"},{"id":14042,"image":"","name":"明石圣子","desc":"美术监督"},{"id":3579,"image":"","name":"高仓佳彦","desc":"作画监督"},{"id":1526,"image":"","name":"熊谷正弘","desc":"摄影监督"},{"id":3685,"image":"","name":"佐佐木政胜","desc":"原画"}],"relations":[{"id":126199,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/d1/b3/126199_I2mTm.jpg","title":"哆啦a梦特别篇","type":"主线故事","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/126199"},{"id":455,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/82/1f/455_k1261.jpg","title":"ドラえもん のび太の創世日記","type":"其他","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/455"}]}